{"id":193239,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/11/译者-《译者》每日原文推荐-2011111/","date":"2011-11-02T05:00:42Z","modified":"2011-11-02T05:00:42Z","title":"译者 | 《译者》每日原文推荐 &#8211; 2011/11/1","content":"<p><p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">以下为每日原文推荐。如果你有兴趣，请参与翻译并将译文寄给</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://yyyyiiii.blogspot.com/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《译者》</span></a><span> </span><b>(</b></span><span><b><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"mailto:iyizhe@gmail.com\"><span>iyizhe@gmail.com</span></a>)</span></b></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">以便与大家共享。欢迎使用</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feedburner.google.com/fb/a/mailverify?uri=yizhe&#038;loc=en_US\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">邮件组</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">、</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://goo.gl/f1NDK\">Google Reader</a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">和推特（</span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#!/yigroup\">@yigroup</a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#!/xiaomi2020\">@xiaomi2020</a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">）跟踪我们的最新消息。</span></span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span> </span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【时政热点】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美联社：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://goo.gl/6Igtf\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国卡车爆炸造成至少</span>7<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">人死亡，</span>200<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">人受伤</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《纽约时报》：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://nyti.ms/sm8Dyq\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">对艾未未被政府罚款</span>240<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">万美元的报道</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">“在这场造恶法与立良法的拉锯战中，表达是金，沉默是死。”</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">路透社：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://goo.gl/6pnTR\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">陈光诚的支持者在北京向公安部请愿</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，抗议临沂地方当局软禁陈光诚，阻拦、殴打前去探望他的人。</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《基督教科学箴言报》：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.csmonitor.com/World/Asia-Pacific/2011/1101/China-human-rights-activists-beaten-for-trying-to-visit-Chen-Guangcheng\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">关于中国人权活动分子造访陈光诚被打的报道</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《每日电讯报》：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/china/8862551/Chinese-police-take-on-lost-generation-grandparents.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国警察对爷爷奶奶辈儿的抗议者下手</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——在上海市中心一家法院外抗议的当年知青一代，被大批警察迅速驱散。</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《华尔街日报》：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://on.wsj.com/tnyZul\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">党内红色明星的发飙，显示北京正孕育着风暴</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——薄熙来对外省报纸编辑的讲话，是党内斗争的反映。</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《时代》周刊：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://ti.me/t1tcRc\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">为什么中国想要帮助欧元区摆脱困境</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">？——北京面临一个十年前难以想象的机会，世界实力格局可能从此改变</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《商业周刊》：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://buswk.co/tgtlxN\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">蒙娜丽莎挂着中国的墙上会很好看</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——如果你是只墙上的飞蝇，或许会无意中听到中国领导人关于拯救欧元区的如下对话</span><span>&#8230; </span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【国际外交】</span></span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">外交关系委员会：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://on.cfr.org/prY5eu\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">应对中国周边的不稳定性</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">（</span><span>70</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">页正文</span><span>PDF</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">）——美国一家智库的报告，探讨如何预防中美之间在北韩、缅甸、巴基斯坦和中亚问题上出现大危机</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《明镜》周刊：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://spon.de/adu10\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">反对向中国妥协的声音越来越高</span></a> </span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【经济金融】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《卫报》：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://gu.com/p/333yp/tw\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">清华外籍教授警告欧洲说，中国更像是狂奔的大笨狼，而不是万能的超人</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span> </span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【生活百态】</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《商业周刊》：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://buswk.co/sddnyb\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">黄金周的游客使澳门赌博业收入创下新纪录</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——十月份澳门赌场收入比去年上升</span><span>42%</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，达</span><span>34</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">亿美元</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《纽约时报》：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://nyti.ms/sWYO3E\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">华裔美军士兵之死，在唐人街引起关注</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——</span><span>19</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">岁的丹尼・陈死于阿富汗。是自杀还是他杀，目前尚不清楚。</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span></span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><i>发送邮件至 yyyyiiii+subscribe@googlegroups.com 即可订阅译文；到iTunes 中搜索“译者”即可订阅和下载译者播客Podcast；点击<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://yyyyiiii.blogspot.com/p/download.html\">这里</a>可以播放和下载所有译者已公开的视频、音频和杂志。（下载需翻墙）。</i><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/5425822223623422432-2489621075495196839?l=yyyyiiii.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=738338\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"738338\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value